FinExecutive is the first job-searching and recruiting platform in Russia for professionals in finance, investments, advisory and consulting.
FinExecutive was created by a Team of finance professionals with over 25 years of combined experience in investments, corporate finance and advisory. We deeply understand the needs of job-seekers in these fields.

This is why:
Each job submitted for posting undergoes thorough screening. FinExecutive does not post jobs with low salaries
FinExecutive is focused on the niche audience of highly qualified professionals, leading companies and recruiters
User interface is simple and functional
Search parameters are specifically tailored
FinExecutive provides confidentiality settings for job-seekers and employers
Other job websites have broad generic coverage and do not fully reflect the specific requirements of employers and job-seekers in the finance profession. FinExecutive allows to find jobs and candidates in the niche finance/business fields more effectively.
